  "title": "<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Evolution occurs ONLY when XP milesto",
  "content": "<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Evolution occurs ONLY when XP milestones are met.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Each evolution grants a new skill or ability.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Final evolution unlocks a unique “Archetype Signature Item.”</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Example: The Archivist’s Evolution Path</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Evolution Level</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>XP Required</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Unlocked Ability</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Stage 1 – The Apprentice</div>",
